name: Neurolinks Live
description:
New art every click! The metaphor of the memorizing information process (note the intensity and blur). Live Generatie Art in a browser.

For full experience: open this script directly on IPFS so you can see a full URL with:
• &seed=726197 — seed for pseudo random image generation
• &size=2 — pixel density (from 1 to 3)
• &blur_steps=11 — blurring steps count
• &after_steps=2 — after blurring drawing steps count

Also you can open browser's terminal/console to see additional information.
PS: Thanks to Piter Pasma!
